3:10 PM Defendant Xavier R Williams in court, in custody.  Attorney Hans Peter Koesser in court for Xavier R Williams.  Attorney Azucena C Guizar Ms. in court for State of Wisconsin. Court Reporter Donna Moore. 

Parties are prepared to proceed with plea/sentencing today. 

State puts offer on the record. Defense confirms offer. 

Plea questionnaire filed. Court holds plea colloquy with defendant. 

Plea - Cts. 1 and 3: GUILTY 
State consents to jury waiver. 
Agreement to use complaint for factual basis. 
BTC: GUILTY. Ct. 2 is dismissed but read in. 
Parties give arguments as to sentencing. 

BTC: Ct. 1: 9 months Racine County Jail; imposed and stayed for 18 months of probation; counts to run concurrent to one another, if Revoked.

Conditions of Probation:
Anger management;
No controlled substances;
Must obtain HSED or equivalency;
Full-time employment and/or schooling;
No contact with K.L H; 
Do not drive without a driver's license;
Deft is Ordered to provide a DNA specimen;
Court Costs+ DNA surcharge 

